race.description: Tab Regional Championship Consolation Mbl Pce
race.comment: HEZA DOOZIE (3) has been out of the placings but not too far away in his last two outings. Kicked off his campaign with back-to-back wins, one of them at this circuit and distance when he came from a wider barrier than this. Has the gate speed to take advantage of the good draw so can return to winning form. VINTAGE EDITION (1) has been solid from back row draws in his two starts so far this campaign. Much better served by the ace draw tonight and should be close to peak fitness third-up. VINCENTIUS MAXIMUS (2) didn't do a bad job when fifth from the back row in the heats and is another better served by tonight's barrier. LOVE LOU (8) hasn't been far from the placegetters from similar draws at his last couple.
